nt is activated, so C3 would be part of that.","dimension":2,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.040035,0.078439,0.091495,0.098427,0.10117,0.099307,0.1001,0.093318,0.086925,0.081044,0.070937,0.05881],"unified_progress":[0.05976,0.075173,0.089328,0.096476,0.10247,0.1007,0.098764,0.093026,0.087093,0.078461,0.066849,0.051899]},{"section":14,"text":"Other possibilities?","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033847,0.07481,0.096409,0.10193,0.10015,0.093806,0.092095,0.088974,0.085828,0.087201,0.074896,0.070062],"unified_progress":[0.036234,0.072974,0.08513,0.10071,0.098897,0.095497,0.096043,0.093503,0.089884,0.092361,0.077097,0.061669]},{"section":15,"text":"Maybe ANCA-associated vasculitis, but those usually have different immunofluorescence patterns, like pauci-immune deposits.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027665,0.063837,0.080855,0.093829,0.10207,0.10369,0.10544,0.099581,0.092185,0.090517,0.076945,0.063389],"unified_progress":[0.030031,0.059585,0.080375,0.091122,0.10134,0.10991,0.10522,0.10345,0.097915,0.092794,0.074029,0.054227]},{"section":16,"text":"The elevated creatinine is concerning, but HSP can have renal involvement.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.026267,0.060977,0.077034,0.087181,0.094026,0.09796,0.10254,0.10087,0.097879,0.094796,0.087798,0.072675],"unified_progress":[0.038119,0.060048,0.073457,0.082407,0.091349,0.098091,0.098924,0.10082,0.10029,0.10063,0.088743,0.067125]},{"section":17,"text":"The absence of eosinophils might rule out some other conditions, but HSP doesn't typically have eosinophilia either.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027657,0.063118,0.078379,0.087046,0.092207,0.095391,0.10116,0.10168,0.099489,0.096677,0.088676,0.06852],"unified_progress":[0.031616,0.062896,0.078653,0.087369,0.096367,0.097549,0.10206,0.10164,0.099582,0.10041,0.084512,0.057357]},{"section":18,"text":"The timing (symptoms started a week ago) is acute, which fits with an immune complex-mediated process like HSP.","dimension":9,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033966,0.068865,0.079619,0.086429,0.091168,0.094606,0.096888,0.096479,0.093981,0.094354,0.086704,0.076941],"unified_progress":[0.045014,0.066567,0.075249,0.082626,0.088608,0.093632,0.096702,0.09783,0.097007,0.097666,0.088418,0.070681]},{"section":19,"text":"So putting it all together: the rash, abdominal and joint symptoms, renal findings with proteinuria and elevated creatinine, and the biopsy showing IgA and C3 deposition.","dimension":4,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.027217,0.057255,0.070428,0.078999,0.085716,0.090412,0.095395,0.096029,0.10097,0.10076,0.1024,0.094415],"unified_progress":[0.034297,0.053774,0.067308,0.076701,0.087012,0.094475,0.097269,0.099574,0.10334,0.10339,0.099028,0.083841]},{"section":20,"text":"The most likely diagnosis is Henoch-Sch\u00f6nlein purpura.","dimension":7,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029421,0.054356,0.06262,0.071052,0.07858,0.08378,0.089547,0.091812,0.095024,0.099579,0.10448,0.13975],"unified_progress":[0.033204,0.041611,0.052815,0.062132,0.06916,0.082271,0.085194,0.095794,0.10237,0.10577,0.12337,0.14632]},{"section":21,"text":"<answer> Henoch-Sch\u00f6nlein purpura </answer>","dimension":7,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036042,0.058596,0.059812,0.065141,0.072423,0.079123,0.085438,0.090161,0.094938,0.099542,0.10682,0.15197],"unified_progress":[0.03796,0.040084,0.047296,0.054805,0.061019,0.072013,0.075445,0.088537,0.097597,0.10561,0.13613,0.1835]}]}}